metadata.name: Square Up Meme
metadata.description:
In 2015, a group of friends gathered around for a Floyd Mayweather fight watch party in the Inland Empire, Southern California. Joking in classic streetwear attire, Shannon posed in the cultures "Square Up" posture. The meme photo has gone viral on countless occasions ever since. This authenticated 1/1 NFT of the original untouched photo is offered by Shannon and his community.

2448 x 3264 Pixels

Square Up Meme
